data.description:
Welcome to your dream home in the highly sought-after community of Beachwalk, where luxury living meets resort-style amenities. This exquisite 4,693 square foot gem is nestled in the heart of St. Johns, Florida, offering the perfect blend of comfort and elegance. Beachwalk is renowned for its stunning 14-acre crystal lagoon, setting the stage for a life of leisure and luxury.
As you step through the grand entrance, you'll be greeted by a spacious foyer that sets the tone for the quality and craftsmanship found throughout this home. 

With 4 bedrooms and 5 bathrooms, this residence has been thoughtfully designed to provide the utmost in modern living. 

The 10-foot ceilings throughout create an open and airy ambiance, and you'll marvel at the coffered ceilings in the dining and study areas. The extended master suite is a true retreat, offering a haven of relaxation and convenience with a dedicated laundry entry. The gourmet kitchen features custom cabinets and an extended kitchen island, perfect for hosting and entertaining. Crown molding graces each room, adding a touch of sophistication to the living spaces.
This home is equipped with a built-in generator for peace of mind during any power outage. Upstairs, a large bonus room with a wet bar provides endless possibilities for recreation and entertainment.

Convenience is key at Beachwalk, as this community is located near a plethora of shopping and dining options. Easy access to major highways ensures quick trips to the historic city of St. Augustine or the vibrant city of Jacksonville.
